# Austin Darrow

## Enterprise Software Engineer Enterprise Software

Email: **[adarrow@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:adarrow@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Austin Darrow joined the TACC Enterprise Software group in 2023 after a successful internship for the Life Sciences Computing group. He is currently working on the redesign of the TACC Allocation System (TAS). Prior to the internship, he taught high school English for four years.

### Education

**B.A., English**  

University of Texas at Austin